snippet.textDisplay:
I regret only finding out about this song last night. And I don't know how many times I've played this video and shed tears every now and then.

This is truly a gift from a beautiful human being. Rahat sings like a sweet man who is confused about expressing the beauty of the girl he loves. Momina sings like a gift package for men who dream of a sweet girl.

I read this song was sung by a Pakistani and the lyrics were written by an Indian poet. If this song had been made earlier, maybe India and Pakistan would not have been separated.

Sending  tons of love from Indonesia.
